cleaned_text: Welcome to Balance Integrative Health & Wellness Our mission is to treat the health and wellness of the whole person. We make it a priority to spend a great deal of time with each patient to find the root cause of their health concerns. This healing moves beyond conventional medicine as we use an integrative approach to connect mind, body and spirit for the ultimate health and wellbeing of our patients.
